OL,3,CCharities cautiously welcome
OL,4,Cunfreezing of housing benefit in
OL,5,Cautumn statement
OL,7,FCouncils and housing charities have
OL,8,Fbroadly welcomed the expected
OL,9,Funfreezing of housing benefit
OL,10,Fannounced in the autumn statement,
OL,11,Fbut there are concerns over how
OL,12,Fquickly it will take effect and how
OL,13,Flong it will last.
OL,15,FThe chancellor confirmed the rise in
OL,16,FLocal Housing Allowance (LHA) rates -
OL,17,Fwhich determine the level of support
OL,18,Fin each area of England - to cover
OL,19,Fthe cheapest 30% of market rents, as
OL,20,Ffirst reported by ITV News last week.
